2:
Yahweh is a mighty king in Jerusalem;
\q2 he is also the supreme ruler of all the people groups.
\q2

4:
He is a mighty king who loves what is just;
\q2 he has acted justly and fairly in Israel.
\q1

9:
Praise Yahweh, our God,
\q2 and worship him at the temple on his sacred hill;
\q2 it is right to do that because Yahweh, our God, is holy!
